name: 死 (Shi) Means “Death”
description: I've seen too many deaths lately. I've seen a lot of deaths lately. It made me think, is death actually something dark and scary? Or is it because we don't know what lies after death? Maybe we will go through a colorful tunnel, full of celebration, while looking through the windows of memories of our previous lives, then find the true meaning of happiness that we never knew before at the end of the tunnel.
